data.description: Move-in ready! Features include: replacement windows throughout; a half-bath on the main floor; a formal dining area for entertaining; a bright, light filled living room; and a spacious eat-in kitchen with ample cabinet space and stainless steel appliances. Extra storage available in basement & in the 2.5 car garage. Bonus rec room in basement expands living or gaming space! Large fenced-in backyard w/ patio is perfect for summer entertaining. Conveniently located near restaurants, golf courses and parks. PHOTOS WILL BE POSTED WHEN AVAILABLE.
